data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home situated on a spacious 1.29-acre lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed kitchen with an abundance of cabinets, perfect for the home chef. The custom-designed bathrooms add a touch of luxury to this property, featuring modern fixtures and elegant finishes. The master bathroom boasts a large soaker tub, ideal for relaxation. Outside, the property is partially fenced, offering privacy and security. With a blend of modern amenities and a generous lot, this home is the perfect combination of comfort and space. Hurricane windows and shutters. Hot water on demand. Whole home plumbing and electric updated in 2019. Hot water on demand. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
